      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FERNCO NEL NZ (2) has looked good in winning his two starts here off a let-up, last week drawing on the back line and using the sprint lane to get home by 3.5m. His record at this longer distance stands at five from six and he should get the favours from this draw so can take this next step. WHOS DELIGHT NZ (3) backs up after he came from a 20m handicap for fourth here on Tuesday and looks suited back to a mobile start having led for a 1.5m second at this circuit and distance prior. Draws well and could be dangerous. XPRESS PARTY (1) did a good job to place last time out and the inside draw could see him competitive again. HES NO ROMEO NZ (4) was solid in his first local appearance here last week. Up in distance and has claims off a Melton win last month.",
